Package com.noctarius.borabora.builder.encoder.semantictag

This package contains the interface definitions for the Builder API com.noctarius.borabora.spi.builder for all built-in semantic tag data types.

Package com.noctarius.borabora.builder.encoder.semantictag Description

This package contains the interface definitions for the Builder API com.noctarius.borabora.spi.builder for all built-in semantic tag data types. For more information please see the Javadoc of the available API support TagSupport.
See Also:
TagSupport, com.noctarius.borabora.spi.builder
